@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_figtrh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(tmp + 0.40)) * ((v2 + 0.70 - v2 + 0.94) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.36)))
    v0 = wp.cos((0.97 * wp.sin(v1 + 0.99)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v1 + 0.88 / v2 + 0.56)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.20)) * v0)
    data[tid] = v0
